620106,125,1037,33,45,1,90,11,"Yaṃ etaṃ vittañca ratanañca pakāsitaṃ, ettha ekampi buddharatanena sadisaṃ ratanaṃ nevatthi. "
620107,125,1037,46,99,1,390,44,"Yampi hi taṃ cittīkataṭṭhena ratanaṃ, seyyathidaṃ– rañño cakkavattissa cakkaratanaṃ maṇiratanañca, yamhi uppanne mahājano na aññattha cittīkāraṃ karoti, na koci pupphagandhādīni gahetvā yakkhaṭṭhānaṃ vā bhūtaṭṭhānaṃ vā gacchati, sabbopi jano cakkaratanamaṇiratanameva cittiṃ karoti pūjeti, taṃ taṃ varaṃ pattheti, patthitapatthitañcassa ekaccaṃ samijjhati, tampi ratanaṃ buddharatanena samaṃ natthi. "
620108,125,1037,100,107,1,51,6,"Yadi hi cittīkataṭṭhena ratanaṃ, tathāgatova ratanaṃ. "
620109,125,1037,108,126,1,107,16,"Tathāgate hi uppanne ye keci mahesakkhā devamanussā, na te aññatra cittīkāraṃ karonti, na kañci aññaṃ pūjenti. "
620110,125,1037,127,142,1,141,14,"Tathā hi brahmā sahampati sinerumattena ratanadāmena tathāgataṃ pūjesi, yathābalañca aññe devā manussā ca bimbisārakosalarājaanāthapiṇḍikādayo. "
620111,125,1037,143,160,1,174,16,"Parinibbutampi ca bhagavantaṃ uddissa channavutikoṭidhanaṃ vissajjetvā asokamahārājā sakalajambudīpe caturāsīti vihārasahassāni patiṭṭhāpesi, ko pana vādo aññesaṃ cittīkārānaṃ. "
620112,125,1037,161,173,1,159,12,Apica kassaññassa parinibbutassāpi jātibodhidhammacakkappavattanaparinibbānaṭṭhānāni paṭimācetiyādīni vā uddissa evaṃ cittīkāragarukāro vattati yathā bhagavato. 
620113,125,1037,174,179,1,52,5,Evaṃ cittīkataṭṭhenāpi tathāgatasamaṃ ratanaṃ natthi. 
620114,125,1038,2,12,1,66,8,"Tathā yampi taṃ mahagghaṭṭhena ratanaṃ, seyyathidaṃ– kāsikaṃ vatthaṃ. "
620115,125,1038,13,14,1,7,1,Yathāha–
620116,125,1038,15,35,1,122,13,"‘‘ jiṇṇampi, bhikkhave, kāsikaṃ vatthaṃ vaṇṇavantañceva hoti sukhasamphassañca mahagghañcā’’ ti, tampi buddharatanena samaṃ natthi. "
620117,125,1038,36,43,1,50,6,"Yadi hi mahagghaṭṭhena ratanaṃ, tathāgatova ratanaṃ. "
620118,125,1038,44,59,1,108,13,"Tathāgato hi yesaṃ paṃsukampi paṭiggaṇhāti, tesaṃ taṃ mahapphalaṃ hoti mahānisaṃsaṃ, seyyathāpi asokassa rañño. "
620119,125,1038,60,62,1,21,2,Idamassa mahagghatāya. 
620120,125,1038,63,71,1,78,8,Evaṃ mahagghatāvacane cettha dosābhāvasādhakaṃ idaṃ tāva suttapadaṃ veditabbaṃ–
620121,125,1039,2,16,1,127,12,"‘ ‘ Yesaṃ kho pana so paṭiggaṇhāti cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ, tesaṃ taṃ mahapphalaṃ hoti mahānisaṃsaṃ. "
620122,125,1039,17,20,1,28,3,Idamassa mahagghatāya vadāmi. 
620123,125,1039,21,49,1,97,12,"Seyyathāpi taṃ, bhikkhave, kāsikaṃ vatthaṃ mahagghaṃ, tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmī’’ ti( a. ni.3.100). "
620124,125,1040,2,7,1,51,5,Evaṃ mahagghaṭṭhenāpi tathāgatasamaṃ ratanaṃ natthi. 
620125,125,1041,2,7,1,35,5,Tathā yampi taṃ atulaṭṭhena ratanaṃ. 
620126,125,1041,8,40,1,292,26,"Seyyathidaṃ– rañño cakkavattissa cakkaratanaṃ uppajjati indanīlamaṇimayanābhi sattaratanamayasahassāraṃ pavāḷamayanemi, rattasuvaṇṇamayasandhi, yassa dasannaṃ dasannaṃ arānaṃ upari ekaṃ muṇḍāraṃ hoti vātaṃ gahetvā saddakaraṇatthaṃ, yena kato saddo sukusalappatāḷitapañcaṅgikatūriyasaddo viya hoti. "
620127,125,1041,41,63,1,151,19,"Yassa nābhiyā ubhosu passesu dve sīhamukhāni honti, abbhantaraṃ sakaṭacakkasseva susiraṃ, tassa kattā vā kāretā vā natthi, kammapaccayena ututo samuṭṭhāti. "
620128,125,1041,64,127,1,501,56,"Yaṃ rājā dasavidhaṃ cakkavattivattaṃ pūretvā tadahuposathe pannarase puṇṇamadivase sīsaṃnhāto uposathiko uparipāsādavaragato sīlāni sodhento nisinno puṇṇacandaṃ viya sūriyaṃ viya ca uṭṭhentaṃ passati, yassa dvādasayojanato saddo suyyati, yojanato vaṇṇo dissati, yaṃ mahājanena‘‘ dutiyo maññe cando sūriyo vā uṭṭhito’’ ti ativiya kotūhalajātena dissamānaṃ nagarassa upari āgantvā rañño antepurassa pācīnapasse nātiuccaṃ nātinīcaṃ hutvā mahājanassa gandhapupphādīhi pūjetuṃ yuttaṭṭhāne akkhāhataṃ viya tiṭṭhati. "
620129,125,1042,2,17,1,143,14,"Tadeva anubandhamānaṃ hatthiratanaṃ uppajjati, sabbaseto rattapādo sattappatiṭṭho iddhimā vehāsaṅgamo uposathakulā vā chaddantakulā vā āgacchati. "
620130,125,1042,18,28,1,103,9,"Uposathakulā āgacchanto hi sabbajeṭṭho āgacchati, chaddantakulā sabbakaniṭṭho sikkhitasikkho damathūpeto. "
620131,125,1042,29,39,1,108,10,So dvādasayojanaṃ parisaṃ gahetvā sakalajambudīpaṃ anusaṃyāyitvā purepātarāsameva sakaṃ rājadhāniṃ āgacchati. 
620132,125,1043,2,14,1,112,11,"Tampi anubandhamānaṃ assaratanaṃ uppajjati, sabbaseto rattapādo kākasīso muñjakeso valāhakassa rājakulā āgacchati. "
620133,125,1043,15,17,1,33,2,Sesamettha hatthiratanasadisameva. 
620134,125,1044,2,6,1,42,4,Tampi anubandhamānaṃ maṇiratanaṃ uppajjati. 
620135,125,1044,7,45,1,280,30,"So hoti maṇi veḷuriyo subho jātimā aṭṭhaṃso suparikammakato āyāmato cakkanābhisadiso, vepullapabbatā āgacchati, so caturaṅgasamannāgatepi andhakāre rañño dhajaggato yojanaṃ obhāseti, yassobhāsena manussā‘‘ divā’’ ti maññamānā kammante payojenti, antamaso kunthakipillikaṃ upādāya passanti. "
620136,125,1045,2,7,1,43,4,Tampi anubandhamānaṃ itthiratanaṃ uppajjati. 
620137,125,1045,8,52,1,340,36,"Pakatiaggamahesī vā hoti, uttarakuruto vā āgacchati maddarājakulato vā, atidīghādichadosavivajjitā atikkantā mānusaṃ vaṇṇaṃ appattā dibbaṃ vaṇṇaṃ, yassā rañño sītakāle uṇhāni gattāni honti, uṇhakāle sītāni, satadhā phoṭitatūlapicuno viya samphasso hoti, kāyato candanagandho vāyati, mukhato uppalagandho, pubbuṭṭhāyitādianekaguṇasamannāgatā ca hoti. "
620138,125,1046,2,25,1,199,20,"Tampi anubandhamānaṃ gahapatiratanaṃ uppajjati rañño pakatikammakaro seṭṭhi, yassa cakkaratane uppannamatte dibbaṃ cakkhu pātubhavati, yena samantato yojanamatte nidhiṃ passati sassāmikampi assāmikampi. "
620139,125,1046,26,47,1,103,14,"So rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā pavāreti‘‘ appossukko tvaṃ, deva, hohi, ahaṃ te dhanena dhanakaraṇīyaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
620140,125,1047,2,22,1,218,18,"Tampi anubandhamānaṃ pariṇāyakaratanaṃ uppajjati rañño pakatijeṭṭhaputto, cakkaratane uppannamatte atirekapaññāveyyattiyena samannāgato hoti, dvādasayojanāya parisāya cetasā cittaṃ parijānitvā niggahapaggahasamattho hoti. "
620141,125,1047,23,27,1,33,4,So rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā pavāreti–
620142,125,1047,28,44,1,56,9,"‘‘ appossukko tvaṃ, deva, hohi, ahaṃ te rajjaṃ anusāsissāmī’’ ti. "
