620170,125,1052,131,146,1,122,14,"Puna rañño gamanacitte uppanne purimanayeneva saddaṃ karontaṃ gacchati, yaṃ sutvā dvādasayojanikāpi parisā ākāsena gacchati. "
620171,125,1052,147,161,1,134,13,"Cakkaratanaṃ anupubbena puratthimaṃ samuddaṃ ajjhogāhati, tasmiṃ ajjhogāhante udakaṃ yojanappamāṇaṃ apagantvā bhittīkataṃ viya tiṭṭhati. "
