620517,125,1108,162,183,1,81,13,"‘‘ Sādhu, bhante, pabbājetha vā maṃ, yaṃ vā icchatha, taṃ katvā pariyosānaṃ jānāpethā’’ ti. "
620518,125,1108,184,204,1,132,15,"Te taṃ pabbājetvā kammaṭṭhāne niyojetuṃ asamatthā‘‘ evaṃ te nivāsetabbaṃ, evaṃ pārupitabban’’ tiādinā nayena ābhisamācārikaṃ sikkhāpesuṃ. "
620519,125,1108,205,213,1,81,8,So tattha sikkhanto upanissayasampannattā na cireneva paccekabodhiṃ abhisambujjhi. 
620520,125,1108,214,225,1,92,7,Sakalabārāṇasiyaṃ‘‘ susīmapaccekabuddho’’ ti pākaṭo ahosi lābhaggayasaggappatto sampannaparivāro. 
620521,125,1108,226,233,1,67,7,So appāyukasaṃvattanikassa kammassa katattā na cireneva parinibbāyi. 
620522,125,1108,234,246,1,106,12,Tassa paccekabuddhā ca mahājanakāyo ca sarīrakiccaṃ katvā dhātuto gahetvā nagaradvāre thūpaṃ patiṭṭhāpesuṃ. 
620523,125,1109,2,44,1,255,33,"Atha kho saṅkho brāhmaṇo‘‘ putto me ciragato, na cassa pavattiṃ jānāmī’’ ti puttaṃ daṭṭhukāmo takkasilāya nikkhamitvā anupubbena bārāṇasiṃ patvā mahājanakāyaṃ sannipatitaṃ disvā‘‘ addhā bahūsu ekopi me puttassa pavattiṃ jānissatī’’ ti cintento upasaṅkamitvā pucchi–"
620524,125,1109,45,62,1,68,12,"‘‘ susīmo nāma māṇavo idha āgato atthi, api nu tassa pavattiṃ jānāthā’’ ti? "
620525,125,1109,63,97,1,218,25,"Te‘‘ āma, brāhmaṇa, jānāma, asmiṃ nagare brāhmaṇassa santike tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū hutvā paccekabuddhānaṃ santike pabbajitvā paccekabuddho hutvā anupādisesāya nibbānadhātuyā parinibbāyi, ayamassa thūpo patiṭṭhāpito’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
620526,125,1109,98,137,1,318,35,"So bhūmiṃ hatthena paharitvā, roditvā ca paridevitvā ca taṃ cetiyaṅgaṇaṃ gantvā tiṇāni uddharitvā uttarasāṭakena vālukaṃ ānetvā, paccekabuddhacetiyaṅgaṇe ākiritvā, kamaṇḍaluto udakena samantato bhūmiṃ paripphositvā vanapupphehi pūjaṃ katvā uttarasāṭakena paṭākaṃ āropetvā thūpassa upari attano chattaṃ bandhitvā pakkāmīti. "
620527,125,1110,2,12,1,91,10,Evaṃ atītaṃ dassetvā taṃ jātakaṃ paccuppannena anusandhento bhikkhūnaṃ dhammakathaṃ kathesi–
620528,125,1110,13,75,1,391,50,"‘‘ siyā kho pana vo, bhikkhave, evamassa añño nūna tena samayena saṅkho brāhmaṇo ahosī’’ ti, na kho panetaṃ evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ, ahaṃ tena samayena saṅkho brāhmaṇo ahosiṃ, mayā susīmassa paccekabuddhassa cetiyaṅgaṇe tiṇāni uddhaṭāni, tassa me kammassa nissandena aṭṭhayojanamaggaṃ vigatakhāṇukaṇṭakaṃ katvā samaṃ suddhamakaṃsu, mayā tattha vālukā okiṇṇā, tassa me nissandena aṭṭhayojanamagge vālukaṃ okiriṃsu. "
620529,125,1110,76,93,1,124,16,"Mayā tattha vanakusumehi pūjā katā, tassa me nissandena navayojanamagge thale ca udake ca nānāpupphehi pupphasantharaṃ akaṃsu. "
620530,125,1110,94,106,1,97,11,"Mayā tattha kamaṇḍaludakena bhūmi paripphositā, tassa me nissandena vesāliyaṃ pokkharavassaṃ vassi. "
620531,125,1110,107,128,1,140,18,"Mayā tasmiṃ cetiye paṭākā āropitā, chattañca baddhaṃ, tassa me nissandena yāva akaniṭṭhabhavanā paṭākā ca āropitā, chattātichattāni ca ussitāni. "
620532,125,1110,129,151,1,149,16,"Iti kho, bhikkhave, ayaṃ mayhaṃ pūjāviseso neva buddhānubhāvena nibbatto, na nāgadevabrahmānubhāvena, apica kho appamattakapariccāgānubhāvena nibbatto’’ ti. "
620533,125,1110,152,155,1,39,3,Dhammakathāpariyosāne imaṃ gāthamabhāsi–
620534,125,1111,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Mattāsukhapariccāgā, passe ce vipulaṃ sukhaṃ; "
620535,125,1112,2,20,1,50,7,"Caje mattāsukhaṃ dhīro, sampassaṃ vipulaṃ sukhan’’ ti.( dha. pa.290); "
