620538,125,1115,2,4,1,21,2,2 . Āmagandhasuttavaṇṇanā 
620539,125,1116,2,8,1,44,3,Sāmākaciṅgūlakacīnakāni {cā}ti āmagandhasuttaṃ. 
620540,125,1116,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
620541,125,1116,12,36,1,226,23,"Anuppanne bhagavati āmagandho nāma brāhmaṇo pañcahi māṇavakasatehi saddhiṃ tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā pabbatantare assamaṃ kārāpetvā vanamūlaphalāhāro hutvā tattha paṭivasati, na kadāci macchamaṃsaṃ khādati. "
620542,125,1116,37,44,1,70,7,Atha tesaṃ tāpasānaṃ loṇambilādīni aparibhuñjantānaṃ paṇḍurogo uppajji. 
620543,125,1116,45,57,1,80,8,Tato te‘‘ loṇambilādisevanatthāya manussapathaṃ gacchāmā’’ ti paccantagāmaṃ sampattā. 
620544,125,1116,58,85,1,200,19,"Tattha manussā tesu pasīditvā nimantetvā bhojesuṃ, katabhattakiccānaṃ nesaṃ mañcapīṭhaparibhogabhājanapādamakkhanādīni upanetvā‘‘ ettha, bhante, vasatha, mā ukkaṇṭhitthā’’ ti vasanaṭṭhānaṃ dassetvā pakkamiṃsu. "
620545,125,1116,86,94,1,78,8,Dutiyadivasepi nesaṃ dānaṃ datvā puna gharapaṭipāṭiyā ekekadivasaṃ dānamadaṃsu. 
620546,125,1116,95,115,1,124,13,"Tāpasā catumāsaṃ tattha vasitvā loṇambilādisevanāya thirabhāvappattasarīrā hutvā‘‘ mayaṃ, āvuso, gacchāmā’’ ti manussānaṃ ārocesuṃ. "
620547,125,1116,116,120,1,36,4,Manussā tesaṃ telataṇḍulādīni adaṃsu. 
620548,125,1116,121,127,1,40,6,Te tāni ādāya attano assamameva agamaṃsu. 
620549,125,1116,128,134,1,52,6,Tañca gāmaṃ tatheva saṃvacchare saṃvacchare āgamiṃsu. 
620550,125,1116,135,149,1,110,13,"Manussāpi tesaṃ āgamanakālaṃ viditvā dānatthāya taṇḍulādīni sajjetvāva acchanti, āgate ca ne tatheva sammānenti. "
620551,125,1117,2,25,1,225,23,Atha bhagavā loke uppajjitvā pavattitavaradhammacakko anupubbena sāvatthiṃ gantvā tattha viharanto tesaṃ tāpasānaṃ upanissayasampattiṃ disvā tato nikkhamma bhikkhusaṅghaparivuto cārikaṃ caramāno anupubbena taṃ gāmaṃ anuppatto. 
620552,125,1117,26,31,1,43,5,Manussā bhagavantaṃ disvā mahādānāni adaṃsu. 
620553,125,1117,32,36,1,28,4,Bhagavā tesaṃ dhammaṃ desesi. 
620554,125,1117,37,54,1,124,14,"Te tāya dhammadesanāya appekacce sotāpannā, ekacce sakadāgāmino, ekacce anāgāmino ahesuṃ, ekacce pabbajitvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇiṃsu. "
620555,125,1117,55,59,1,38,4,Bhagavā punadeva sāvatthiṃ paccāgamāsi. 
620556,125,1117,60,66,1,33,6,Atha te tāpasā taṃ gāmaṃ āgamiṃsu. 
620557,125,1117,67,73,1,52,6,Manussā tāpase disvā na pubbasadisaṃ kotūhalamakaṃsu. 
620558,125,1117,74,77,1,20,3,Tāpasā taṃ pucchiṃsu–
620559,125,1117,78,111,1,174,24,"‘‘ kiṃ, āvuso, ime manussā na pubbasadisā, kiṃ nu kho ayaṃ gāmo rājadaṇḍena upadduto, udāhu dubbhikkhena, udāhu amhehi sīlādiguṇehi sampannataro koci pabbajito imaṃ gāmamanuppatto’’ ti? "
620560,125,1117,112,114,1,9,2,Te āhaṃsu–
620561,125,1117,115,143,1,134,18,"‘‘ na, bhante, rājadaṇḍena, na dubbhikkhenāyaṃ gāmo upadduto, apica buddho loke uppanno, so bhagavā bahujanahitāya dhammaṃ desento idhāgato’’ ti. "
620562,125,1118,2,16,1,56,7,"Taṃ sutvā āmagandhatāpaso‘‘ buddhoti, gahapatayo, vadethā’’ ti?"
620563,125,1118,17,46,1,136,18,"‘‘ Buddhoti, bhante, vadāmā’’ ti tikkhattuṃ vatvā‘‘ ghosopi kho eso dullabho lokasmiṃ, yadidaṃ buddho’’ ti attamano attamanavācaṃ nicchāretvā pucchi–"
620564,125,1118,47,62,1,55,10,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho so buddho āmagandhaṃ bhuñjati, na bhuñjatī’’ ti?"
620565,125,1118,63,73,1,22,4,"‘‘ Ko, bhante, āmagandho’’ ti?"
