620570,125,1118,115,117,1,12,2,Puna cintesi–
620571,125,1118,118,133,1,77,10,"‘‘ buddhānaṃ pātubhāvo nāma dullabho, gantvā buddhaṃ disvā pucchitvā jānissāmī’’ ti. "
620572,125,1118,134,156,1,178,21,"Tato yena bhagavā gato, taṃ maggaṃ manusse pucchitvā vacchagiddhinī gāvī viya turitaturito sabbattha ekarattivāsena sāvatthiṃ anuppatvā jetavanameva pāvisi saddhiṃ sakāya parisāya. "
620573,125,1118,157,165,1,65,8,Bhagavāpi tasmiṃ samaye dhammadesanatthāya āsane nisinno eva hoti. 
620574,125,1118,166,173,1,77,7,Tāpasā bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamma tuṇhībhūtā anabhivādetvāva ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
620575,125,1118,174,188,1,74,10,Bhagavā‘‘ kacci vo isayo khamanīyan’’ tiādinā nayena tehi saddhiṃ paṭisammodi. 
620576,125,1118,189,199,1,40,5,"Tepi‘‘ khamanīyaṃ, bho gotamā’’ tiādimāhaṃsu. "
