620597,125,1119,160,189,1,226,24,"Bodhisattopi aparena samayena ghare ṭhitoyeva ānāpānassatiṃ pariggahetvā cattāri jhānāni abhiññāyo ca uppādetvā pāsādena bodhimaṇḍasamīpaṃ gantvā‘‘ puna pāsādo yathāṭhāneyeva patiṭṭhātū’’ ti adhiṭṭhāsi, so sakaṭṭhāneyeva patiṭṭhāsi. "
