620884,125,1163,2,10,1,30,5,Evaṃ me sutan ti maṅgalasuttaṃ. 
620885,125,1163,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
620886,125,1163,14,31,1,191,16,"Jambudīpe kira tattha tattha nagaradvārasanthāgārasabhādīsu mahājanā sannipatitvā hiraññasuvaṇṇaṃ datvā nānappakāraṃ sītāharaṇādibāhirakakathaṃ kathāpenti, ekekā kathā catumāsaccayena niṭṭhāti. "
620887,125,1163,32,36,1,41,4,Tattha ekadivasaṃ maṅgalakathā samuṭṭhāsi–
620888,125,1163,37,60,1,92,15,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho maṅgalaṃ, kiṃ diṭṭhaṃ maṅgalaṃ, sutaṃ maṅgalaṃ, mutaṃ maṅgalaṃ, ko maṅgalaṃ jānātī’’ ti? "
