620896,125,1165,27,52,1,146,21,"Yadi tena diṭṭhaṃ maṅgalaṃ siyā, sabbampi maṅgalaṃ siyā, tasmā na diṭṭhaṃ maṅgalaṃ, apica kho pana sutaṃ maṅgalaṃ, sutaṃ nāma abhimaṅgalasammato saddo. "
