621402,125,1332,2,22,1,143,17,"Idha pana bhikkhuno senāsanaṃ pāpuṇāti, so teneva santussati, puna aññaṃ sundaratarampi pāpuṇantaṃ na gaṇhāti, ayamassa senāsane yathālābhasantoso. "
621403,125,1332,23,51,1,234,25,"Atha pana ābādhiko hoti, nivātasenāsane vasanto ativiya pittarogādīhi āturīyati, so sabhāgassa bhikkhuno taṃ datvā tassa pāpuṇanake savātasītalasenāsane vasitvā samaṇadhammaṃ karontopi santuṭṭhova hoti, ayamassa senāsane yathābalasantoso. "
