622272,125,1525,15,37,1,174,18,Bhagavā sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambujjhitvā bodhimaṇḍato anupubbena kapilavatthuṃ gantvā tattha rāhulakumārena‘‘ dāyajjaṃ me samaṇa dehī’’ ti dāyajjaṃ yācito sāriputtattheraṃ āṇāpesi–
622273,125,1525,38,45,1,26,3,‘‘ rāhulakumāraṃ pabbājehī’’ ti. 
