622278,125,1525,124,166,1,290,33,"Tattha paṭhamagāthāyaṃ ayaṃ saṅkhepattho‘‘ kacci tvaṃ, rāhula, abhiṇhaṃ saṃvāsahetu jātiādīnaṃ aññatarena vatthunā na paribhavasi paṇḍitaṃ, ñāṇapadīpassa dhammadesanāpadīpassa ca dhāraṇato ukkādhāro manussānaṃ kacci apacito tayā, kacci niccaṃ pūjito tayā’’ ti āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ sandhāya bhaṇati. "
