622285,125,1528,19,30,1,56,6,‘ saddhāya gharā nikkhammā’’’ ti vuccate– nekkhammādhimuttattā. 
622286,125,1528,31,60,1,290,29,Ayañhi āyasmā dīgharattaṃ nekkhammādhimutto padumuttarasammāsambuddhassa puttaṃ uparevataṃ nāma sāmaṇeraṃ disvā saṅkho nāma nāgarājā hutvā satta divase dānaṃ datvā tathābhāvaṃ patthetvā tato pabhuti patthanāsampanno abhinīhārasampanno satasahassakappe pāramiyo pūretvā antimabhavaṃ upapanno. 
622287,125,1528,61,65,1,45,4,Evaṃ nekkhammādhimuttatañcassa bhagavā jānāti. 
