624009,125,1847,89,99,1,68,9,"So hi khīṇāsavamunittā devamanussānaṃ pūjāraho hoti, tasmā evaṃ thuto. "
624010,125,1848,2,24,1,164,18,"535. Evaṃ tatiyagāthāya vuttapañhe vissajjetvā catutthagāthāya vuttapañhesupi yasmā yo catūhi maggañāṇavedehi kilesakkhayaṃ karonto gato, so paramatthato vedagū nāma hoti. "
624011,125,1848,25,36,1,104,10,"Yo ca sabbasamaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ satthasaññitāni vedāni, tāyeva maggabhāvanāya kiccato aniccādivasena viceyya. "
624012,125,1848,37,78,1,221,28,"Tattha chandarāgappahānena tameva sabbaṃ vedamaticca yā vedapaccayā vā aññathā vā uppajjanti vedanā , tāsu sabbavedanāsu vītarāgo hoti, tasmā tamatthaṃ dassento‘‘ idaṃ pattinan’’ ti avatvā‘‘ vedānī’’ ti gāthāya paṭhamapañhaṃ byākāsi. "
624013,125,1848,79,100,1,150,19,"Yasmā vā yo pavicayapaññāya vedāni viceyya, tattha chandarāgappahānena sabbaṃ vedamaticca vattati, so satthasaññitāni vedāni gato ñāto atikkanto ca hoti. "
624014,125,1848,101,112,1,71,10,"Yo vedanāsu vītarāgo, sopi vedanāsaññitāni vedāni gato atikkanto ca hoti. "
624015,125,1848,113,133,1,110,15,"Vedāni gatotipi vedagū, tasmā tampi atthaṃ dassento‘‘ idaṃ pattinan’’ ti avatvā imāya gāthāya paṭhamapañhaṃ byākāsi. "
624016,125,1849,2,83,1,537,61,"536. Yasmā pana dutiyapañhe‘‘ anuvidito’’ ti anubuddho vuccati, so ca anuvicca papañcanāmarūpaṃ ajjhattaṃ attano santāne taṇhāmānadiṭṭhibhedaṃ papañcaṃ tappaccayā nāmarūpañca aniccānupassanādīhi anuvicca anuviditvā, na kevalañca ajjhattaṃ, bahiddhā ca rogamūlaṃ, parasantāne ca imassa nāmarūparogassa mūlaṃ avijjābhavataṇhādiṃ, tameva vā papañcaṃ anuvicca tāya bhāvanāya sabbesaṃ rogānaṃ mūlabandhanā, sabbasmā vā rogānaṃ mūlabandhanā, avijjābhavataṇhādibhedā, tasmā eva vā papañcā pamutto hoti, tasmā taṃ dassento‘‘ anuviccā’’ ti gāthāya dutiyapañhaṃ byākāsi. "
