624838,125,2045,29,42,1,69,11,"Atha kho {kokāliko}ti ettha pana ko ayaṃ kokāliko, kasmā ca upasaṅkamīti? "
624839,125,2045,43,67,1,165,18,"Vuccate– ayaṃ kira kokālikaraṭṭhe kokālikanagare kokālikaseṭṭhissa putto pabbajitvā pitarā kārāpite vihāreyeva paṭivasati‘‘ cūḷakokāliko’’ ti nāmena, na devadattassa sisso. "
624840,125,2045,68,78,1,43,6,So hi brāhmaṇaputto‘‘ mahākokāliko’’ ti paññāyi. 
624841,125,2046,2,30,1,263,28,Bhagavati kira sāvatthiyaṃ viharante dve aggasāvakā pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi saddhiṃ janapadacārikaṃ caramānā upakaṭṭhāya vassūpanāyikāya vivekavāsaṃ vasitukāmā te bhikkhū uyyojetvā attano pattacīvaramādāya tasmiṃ janapade taṃ nagaraṃ patvā taṃ vihāraṃ agamaṃsu. 
624842,125,2046,31,38,1,50,7,Tattha te kokālikena saddhiṃ sammoditvā taṃ āhaṃsu–
