625883,125,2236,2,4,1,24,2,5 . Paramaṭṭhakasuttavaṇṇanā 
625884,125,2237,2,11,1,39,3,803. Paramanti {diṭṭhīsū}ti paramaṭṭhakasuttaṃ. 
625885,125,2237,12,14,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
625886,125,2237,15,39,1,150,19,"Bhagavati kira sāvatthiyaṃ viharante nānātitthiyā sannipatitvā attano attano diṭṭhiṃ dīpentā‘‘ idaṃ paramaṃ, idaṃ paraman’’ ti kalahaṃ katvā rañño ārocesuṃ. "
625887,125,2237,40,53,1,74,9,Rājā sambahule jaccandhe sannipātāpetvā‘‘ imesaṃ hatthiṃ dassethā’’ ti āṇāpesi. 
625888,125,2237,54,67,1,75,9,Rājapurisā andhe sannipātāpetvā hatthiṃ purato sayāpetvā‘‘ passathā’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
625889,125,2237,68,73,1,39,5,Te hatthissa ekamekaṃ aṅgaṃ parāmasiṃsu. 
625890,125,2237,74,103,1,101,16,"Tato raññā‘‘ kīdiso, bhaṇe, hatthī’’ ti puṭṭho yo soṇḍaṃ parāmasi, so‘‘ seyyathāpi, mahārāja, naṅgalīsā’’ ti bhaṇi. "
625891,125,2237,104,133,1,129,18,"Ye dantādīni parāmasiṃsu, te itaraṃ‘‘ mā bho rañño purato musā bhaṇī’’ ti paribhāsitvā‘‘ seyyathāpi, mahārāja, bhittikhilo’’ tiādīni āhaṃsu. "
625892,125,2237,134,148,1,64,10,Rājā taṃ sabbaṃ sutvā‘‘ īdiso tumhākaṃ samayo’’ ti titthiye uyyojesi. 
625893,125,2237,149,156,1,57,7,Aññataro piṇḍacāriko taṃ pavattiṃ ñatvā bhagavato ārocesi. 
625894,125,2237,157,193,1,253,29,"Bhagavā tassaṃ aṭṭhuppattiyaṃ bhikkhū āmantetvā‘‘ yathā, bhikkhave, jaccandhā hatthiṃ ajānantā taṃ taṃ aṅgaṃ parāmasitvā vivadiṃsu, evaṃ titthiyā vimokkhantikadhammaṃ ajānantā taṃ taṃ diṭṭhiṃ parāmasitvā vivadantī’’ ti vatvā dhammadesanatthaṃ imaṃ suttamabhāsi. "
625895,125,2238,2,20,1,96,13,Tattha paraman ti diṭṭhīsu {paribbasāno}ti‘‘ idaṃ paraman’’ ti gahetvā sakāya sakāya diṭṭhiyā vasamāno. 
625896,125,2238,21,29,1,56,7,Yaduttari {kurute}ti yaṃ attano satthārādiṃ seṭṭhaṃ karoti. 
625897,125,2238,30,50,1,92,15,Hīnāti aññe tato {sabbamāhā}ti taṃ attano satthārādiṃ ṭhapetvā tato aññe sabbe‘‘ hīnā ime’’ ti āha. 
625898,125,2238,51,61,1,75,9,Tasmā vivādāni {avītivatto}ti tena kāraṇena so diṭṭhikalahe avītivattova hoti. 
625899,125,2239,2,26,1,152,18,804. Dutiyagāthāya attho– evaṃ avītivatto ca yaṃ diṭṭhe sute sīlavate {mute}ti etesu vatthūsu uppannadiṭṭhisaṅkhāte attani pubbe vuttappakāraṃ ānisaṃsaṃ passati. 
625900,125,2239,27,47,1,120,15,Tadeva so tattha sakāya diṭṭhiyā ānisaṃsaṃ‘‘ idaṃ seṭṭhan’’ ti abhinivisitvā aññaṃ sabbaṃ parasatthārādikaṃ nihīnato passati. 
625901,125,2240,2,30,1,173,22,"805. Tatiyagāthāya attho– evaṃ passato cassa yaṃ attano satthārādiṃ nissito aññaṃ parasatthārādiṃ hīnaṃ passati taṃ pana dassanaṃ ganthameva kusalā vadanti, bandhananti vuttaṃ hoti . "
625902,125,2240,31,48,1,109,15,"Yasmā etadeva, tasmā hi diṭṭhaṃva sutaṃ mutaṃ vā sīlabbataṃ bhikkhu na nissayeyya, nābhiniveseyyāti vuttaṃ hoti. "
625903,125,2241,2,28,1,153,20,"806. Catutthagāthāya attho– na kevalaṃ diṭṭhasutādiṃ na nissayeyya, apica kho pana asañjātaṃ uparūpari diṭṭhimpi lokasmiṃ na kappayeyya, na janeyyāti vuttaṃ hoti. "
625904,125,2241,29,30,1,7,1,Kīdisaṃ? 
625905,125,2241,31,48,1,105,15,"Ñāṇena vā sīlavatena vāpi, samāpattiñāṇādinā ñāṇena vā sīlavatena vā yā kappiyati, etaṃ diṭṭhiṃ na kappeyya. "
625906,125,2241,49,70,1,133,18,"Na kevalañca diṭṭhiṃ na kappayeyya, apica kho pana mānenapi jātiādīhi vatthūhi samoti attānamanūpaneyya, hīno na maññetha visesi {vāpī}ti. "
625907,125,2242,2,33,1,194,26,"807. Pañcamagāthāya attho– evañhi diṭṭhiṃ akappento amaññamāno ca attaṃ pahāya anupādiyāno idha vā yaṃ pubbe gahitaṃ, taṃ pahāya aparaṃ aggaṇhanto tasmimpi vuttappakāre ñāṇe duvidhaṃ nissayaṃ no karoti. "
625908,125,2242,34,58,1,190,23,"Akaronto ca sa ve viyattesu nānādiṭṭhivasena bhinnesu sattesu na vaggasārī chandādivasena agacchanadhammo hutvā dvāsaṭṭhiyā diṭṭhīsu kiñcipi diṭṭhiṃ na pacceti, na paccāgacchatīti vuttaṃ hoti. "
625909,125,2243,2,4,1,0,0,808-10. 
