627935,126,103,17,20,1,16,3,Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti–
627936,126,103,21,52,1,146,20,"‘‘ kena tetādiso vaṇṇo’’ tiādinā therena pucchīyatīti pucchā, tāya devatāya katakammaṃ, tassā pucchāya kāritā ācikkhitā vāti sā devatā‘‘ pucchitā’’ ti vuttā. "
627937,126,103,53,62,1,66,8,"Yasmā pucchitā pucchiyamānassa kammassa kāritā, tasmā pañhaṃ puṭṭhā. "
627938,126,103,63,73,1,82,9,"Yasmā ca pucchitā pucchiyamānassa kammassa ācikkhanasabhāvā, tasmā pañhaṃ byākāsīti. "
627939,126,103,74,88,1,75,10,Yassa kammassidaṃ phalan ti idaṃ‘‘ pañhan’’ ti vuttassa atthassa sarūpadassanaṃ. 
627940,126,103,89,111,1,179,20,"Ayaṃ cettha attho– idaṃ pucchantassa pucchiyamānāya ca paccakkhabhūtaṃ anantaraṃ vuttappakāraṃ puññaphalaṃ, yassa kammassa taṃ ñātuṃ icchitattā pañhanti vuttaṃ puññakammaṃ byākāsīti. "
627941,126,104,2,10,1,42,4,5. Ahaṃ {manussesū}tiādi pañhassa byākaraṇākāro. 
627942,126,104,11,17,1,39,6,Tattha ahan ti devatā attānaṃ niddisati.
627943,126,104,18,37,1,98,11,‘‘ Manussesū’’ ti vatvā puna‘‘ manussabhūtā’’ ti vacanaṃ tadā attani manussaguṇānaṃ vijjamānatādassanatthaṃ. 
627944,126,104,38,58,1,178,18,"Yo hi manussajātikova samāno pāṇātipātādiṃ akattabbaṃ katvā daṇḍāraho tattha tattha rājādito hatthacchedādikammakāraṇaṃ pāpuṇanto mahādukkhaṃ anubhavati, ayaṃ manussanerayiko nāma. "
627945,126,104,59,78,1,166,16,"Aparo manussajātikova samāno pubbekatakammunā ghāsacchādanampi na labhati, khuppipāsābhibhūto dukkhabahulo katthaci patiṭṭhaṃ alabhamāno vicarati, ayaṃ manussapeto nāma. "
627946,126,104,79,103,1,255,23,"Aparo manussajātikova samāno parādhīnavutti paresaṃ bhāraṃ vahanto bhinnamariyādo vā anācāraṃ ācaritvā parehi santajjito maraṇabhayabhīto gahananissito dukkhabahulo vicarati hitāhitaṃ ajānanto niddājighacchādukkhavinodanādiparo, ayaṃ manussatiracchāno nāma. "
627947,126,104,104,129,1,258,23,"Yo pana attano hitāhitaṃ jānanto kammaphalaṃ saddahanto hirottappasampanno dayāpanno sabbasattesu saṃvegabahulo akusalakammapathe parivajjento kusalakammapathe samācaranto puññakiriyavatthūni paripūreti, ayaṃ manussadhamme patiṭṭhito paramatthato manusso nāma. "
627948,126,104,130,133,1,19,3,Ayampi tādisā ahosi. 
627949,126,104,134,143,1,37,5,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ manussesu manussabhūtā’’ ti. 
627950,126,104,144,152,1,79,8,Manusse sattanikāye manussabhāvaṃ pattā manussadhammañca appahāya ṭhitāti attho. 
627951,126,105,2,8,1,56,5,"Abbhāgatānan ti abhiāgatānaṃ, sampattaāgantukānanti attho. "
627952,126,105,9,14,1,38,5,Duvidhā hi āgantukā atithi abbhāgatoti. 
627953,126,105,15,22,1,57,6,"Tesu kataparicayo āgantuko atithi, akataparicayo abbhāgato. "
627954,126,105,23,35,1,103,11,"Kataparicayo akataparicayopi vā puretaraṃ āgato atithi, bhojanavelāyaṃ upaṭṭhito sampati āgato abbhāgato. "
627955,126,105,36,43,1,49,6,"Nimantito vā bhattena atithi, animantito abbhāgato. "
627956,126,105,44,65,1,121,15,"Ayaṃ pana akataparicayo animantito sampati āgato ca, taṃ sandhāyāha‘‘ abbhāgatānan’’ ti, garukārena panettha bahuvacanaṃ vuttaṃ. "
627957,126,105,66,70,1,29,4,Āsati nisīdati etthāti āsanaṃ. 
627958,126,105,71,91,1,100,14,"Yaṃkiñci nisīdanayoggaṃ, idha pana pīṭhaṃ adhippetaṃ, tassa ca appakattā anuḷārattā ca‘‘ āsanakan’’ ti āha. "
627959,126,105,92,118,1,212,21,"Adāsin ti‘‘ idamassa therassa dinnaṃ mayhaṃ mahapphalaṃ bhavissati mahānisaṃsan’’ ti sañjātasomanassā kammaṃ kammaphalañca saddahitvā tassa therassa paribhogatthāya adāsiṃ, nirapekkhapariccāgavasena pariccajinti attho. "
627960,126,106,2,10,1,83,7,"Abhivādayin ti abhivādanamakāsiṃ, pañcapatiṭṭhitena dakkhiṇeyyapuggale vandinti anto. "
627961,126,106,11,32,1,116,15,"Vandamānā hi taṃ tāyeva vandanakiriyāya vandiyamānaṃ‘‘ sukhinī hohi, arogā hohī’’ tiādinā āsivādaṃ atthato vadāpesi nāma. "
627962,126,106,33,45,1,117,11,Añjalikaṃ akāsin ti dasanakhasamodhānasamujjalaṃ añjaliṃ sirasi paggaṇhantī guṇavisiṭṭhānaṃ apacāyanaṃ akāsinti attho. 
627963,126,106,46,54,1,69,7,"Yathānubhāvan ti yathābalaṃ, tadā mama vijjamānavibhavānurūpanti attho. "
627964,126,106,55,64,1,94,9,Adāsi dānan ti annapānādideyyadhammapariccāgena dakkhiṇeyyaṃ bhojentī dānamayaṃ puññaṃ pasaviṃ. 
627965,126,107,2,46,1,326,29,"Ettha ca‘‘ ahan’’ ti idaṃ kammassa phalassa ca ekasantatipatitatādassanena sambandhabhāvadassanaṃ,‘‘ manussesu manussabhūtā’’ ti idaṃ tassā puññakiriyāya adhiṭṭhānabhūtasantānavisesadassanaṃ,‘‘ abbhāgatānan’’ ti idaṃ cittasampattidassanañceva khettasampattidassanañca dānassa viya paṭiggahaṇassa ca kiñci anapekkhitvā pavattitabhāvadīpanato."
627966,126,107,47,70,1,131,14,"‘‘ Āsanakaṃ adāsiṃ yathānubhāvañca adāsi dānan’’ ti idaṃ bhogasāradānadassanaṃ,‘‘ abhivādayiṃ añjalikaṃ akāsin’’ ti idaṃ kāyasāradānadassanaṃ. "
627967,126,108,2,11,1,44,5,6. {Tenā}ti tena yathāvuttena puññena hetubhūtena. 
