628886,126,630,2,53,1,413,42,"128. Tattha issā ca maccheramatho paḷāso, nāhosi mayhaṃ {gharamāvasantiyā}ti yā ca agāramajjhe vasantīnaṃ aññāsaṃ itthīnaṃ sampattiādivisayā parasampattiusūyanalakkhaṇā issā, yañca tāvakālikādivasenāpi kiñci yācantānaṃ adātukāmatāya attasampattinigūhanalakkhaṇaṃ macchariyaṃ , yo ca kulapadesādinā parehi yugaggāhalakkhaṇo paḷāso uppajjati, so tividhopi pāpadhammo gehe ṭhitāya mayhaṃ satipi paccayasamavāye nāhosi na uppajji. "
