629172,126,722,49,83,1,233,26,"Taṃ sutvā upāsako‘‘ kāmesu ādīnavaṃ, nekkhamme ca ānisaṃsaṃ sampassantā’’ ti vatvā attano ñāṇabalānurūpaṃ tamatthaṃ vitthārato kathesi, tiṇṇañca ratanānaṃ guṇe pakāsesi, pañcannaṃ sīlānaṃ diṭṭhadhammikaṃ samparāyikañca guṇānisaṃsaṃ pavedesi. "
